@audience fulab agents, musn server
@tone technical
@style pattern

! conclusion: Track off-trail moves and pause when the budget is exceeded.
  + context: Agents drift with repeated reads outside the allowed trail.
  + IF:
    Off-trail count exceeds limit (free + ratio * on-trail).
  + HOWEVER:
    Some exploration is necessary; total blocking hurts progress.
  + THEN:
    Warn as budget nears; pause when exceeded; require clarification or expanded scope to resume.
  + BECAUSE:
    Bounded exploration keeps runs aligned with candidate patterns and scope.
  + NEXT-STEPS:
    - evidence: trail stats per turn (:on, :off, :limit) and any :turn/pause with reason :off-trail.
    - evidence-shape: {:trail {:on :int, :off :int, :limit :double}, :reason {:type :keyword, :note :string}}
